casebody.data:
Andreyko, Appellee, v. City of Cincinnati et al., Appellants.

[Cite as Andreyko v. Cincinnati, 102 Ohio St.3d 1238, 2004-Ohio-3070.]

(No. 2003-1212 Submitted May 25, 2004 Decided June 30, 2004.) Katz, Teller, Brant & Hild and James F. McCarthy III, for appellee. Julia L. McNeil, City Solicitor, Julie F. Bissinger, Chief Counsel, and Frank H. Prouty Jr., Assistant City Solicitor, for appellants.

{¶ 1} The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor and O’Donnell, JJ., concur.
